{color:#bf2600}The duplicated weave follows the Sort Order of Weaves applied on the left pane.{color}

{color:#bf2600}Default Sorting: Sorted by last date and time opened, Descending order – meaning latest weave that was opened is shown on top. This sorting can be changed by the user. {color}

{color:#bf2600}Sort options:{color}

* {color:#bf2600}By Name - based on Folder Name, then Weave Name{color}
** {color:#bf2600}If all starts with Knit or have the similar name, then sort by Date Opened (date and timestamp){color}
* {color:#bf2600}By Date Opened (by me) - based on the date (and time) the Weaves page or any of its sheets was loaded completely{color}
** {color:#bf2600}For same Date Opened, sort by Time Opened{color}
* {color:#bf2600}By Date Created - based on the date (and time) the Weave was created{color}
** {color:#bf2600}For same Date Created, sort by Time Created{color}
* {color:#bf2600}By Date Modified (by all assignees) - based on the date (and time) a change was made to the Weave, its sheets, or dashboards{color}
** {color:#bf2600}For same Date Modified, sort by Time Modified{color}
* {color:#bf2600}By Date Shared - based on the date (and time) the Weave was shared to the user{color}
** {color:#bf2600}For same Date Shared, sort by Time Shared{color}
** {color:#bf2600}If date & time shared are the same, then sort by Date Opened (date and timestamp){color}

{color:#bf2600}See Sort options in {color}[{color:#bf2600}Sort Weaves - KnitWare - Confluence (atlassian.net){color}|https://sourcefitdev.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/KNIT/pages/2241626114/Sort+Weaves]
